				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: AA path<a name="19547"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Feb 6 04 10:59 AM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>Gonna list mine if I can remember them all correctly. They are in order that I got them. I raid more than anything else I do. I'm in a guild that is Cori and TRC away from Time and still farming Ele molds as far as progression.
<br />

<br />
(G) = General
<br />
(A) = Archetype
<br />
(C) = Class
<br />
(P) = PoP
<br />

<br />
Run Speed 3 (G)
<br />
Innate Stamina 3 (G)
<br />
Natural Durability 3 (A)
<br />
Instrument Mastery (C)
<br />
PoP came out, leveled to 63
<br />
Fading Memories (P)
<br />
Instrument Mastery 3 (C)
<br />
Singing Mastery 2 (C)
<br />
Physical Enhancement (C) 
<br />
Mental Clarity 1 (A)
<br />
Extended Notes 3 (C)
<br />
Scionache's Crescendo 3 (P)
<br />
Lightning Reflexes 3 (P)
<br />
Banked enough for Jam Fest 3 (C)
<br />
Harmonious Attack 5 (P)
<br />
Ambidex (P)
<br />
Channeling Focus 1 (A)
<br />
Innate Regeneration 3 (G)
<br />
Jam Fest was fixed and I bought it all the way to 3 (C)
<br />
Ayonae's Tutelage 2 (P)
<br />

<br />
I currently have 18 banked and I plan to purchase IIM and RS1 right off the bat. Then will probably go back and finish SM3 and ISM. Then RS2 and will re-eval at that point where to spend again. But likely to finish up all the combat AA's at that point, then go to all the regens including mana.
<br />

<br />
I have no War Drums yet so kinda wasted 4 points on AT but was given the impression we'd be farming Peregrin till we got drums. I stopped spending there when I realized that wasn't gonna happen.
<br />

<br />
Magelo here if you're wondering:
<br />
http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=26239
<br />

<br />
EDIT: Spelled out the AA's for folks not familiar with them and rearranged Mental Clarity. I didn't buy it till FM.</span></td>
