				<td colspan="2"><span>I just turned 59 bard and i am now going to start on AA's can some walk me through the path.  I have only been playing EQ for 4 months now and i was never PL or tweaked so i have just been grinding it out to get to lv 59 and I really don't understand how the AA tree works do i have to start off with general AA and then work my way to class AA ?? or can i just go right to class AA's ??? And which AA should i get 1st i understand that everyone has a different idea but i will be great to get some kind of idea...thanks for any help</span></td>
