gives you baron/ess
<br />

<br />
Level 61+
<br />
Fade
<br />
CA3(ND at lower STA levels is not as important as dodging a hit all together)
<br />
gives you veteran
<br />

<br />
IM3
<br />
JF1
<br />
SM1 
<br />
will give you impressario/muse
<br />
LR5 (again dodge away)
<br />

