all physical are great, moving JF to 3 is ok but really very minimal return for the 15aa.  That same 15aa in the regens makes a huge difference.  Bellow is a toy for the most part, mez interrupts most casting and rarely is there times that you NEED it(but works hella good on insignia camps for teh Advisor gfluxer)</span></td>
